<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>This type defines a box collision shape. The origin is at the center of the box.</db:para>
<db:note>
<db:para>A non-uniform scaling transformation will scale the x, y and z directions individually. However, combining non-uniform scale and rotation may lead to shearing, which will not be applied to the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick3d-physics-boxshape.xml">BoxShape</db:link>: it will always be a rectilinear box.</db:para>
</db:note>
